<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/chris-elmore> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Chris Elmore was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office on 7 September 2025. He was previously Comptroller of HM Household (Government Whip) between 10 July 2024 and 7 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Bridgend in July 2024."@en .
